'''埃默里大學'''（{{lang-en|Emory University}}），或譯'''艾文理大學'''、'''艾默利大學'''，創校於1836年，為一位於美國[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]][[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]都市地区[[迪卡尔布县_(佐治亚州)|迪卡尔布县]][[德鲁伊山_(喬治亞州)|德鲁伊山]]之私立菁英[[大學|大學]]；另設有牛津校區。1836年[[循道宗|循道宗]]主教[[约翰·埃默里|约翰·埃默里]]创办埃默里学院为其起源<ref name=Emory>{{cite web|title=''Emory'': History & Traditions|url=http://www.emory.edu/home/about/history/index.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924095929/http://www.emory.edu/home/about/history/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1915年学院迁到亚特兰大都市地区，改名为埃默里大学。它是乔治亚州第二老的私立高校<ref>{{cite web|title=''New Georgia Encyclopedia'':Emory University|url=http://www.georgiaencyclopedia.org/articles/education/emory-university|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129091141/https://www.georgiaencyclopedia.org/articles/education/emory-university|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

埃默里大學设有多个学院：埃默里文理学院、[[埃默里大学牛津学院|牛津学院]]、戈伊苏埃塔商学院、莱尼研究生院、法学院、内尔霍奇森伍德拉夫护理学院、[[罗琳斯公共卫生学院|罗琳斯公共卫生学院]]和康德勒神学院。埃默里大學与[[佐治亚理工学院|佐治亚理工学院]]一起运行生物医学工程系，该系与中国[[北京大学|北京大学]]在教育和科研方面合作紧密<ref>{{cite web|title=Georgia Tech / Emory / Peking University BME PhD Program|url=https://bme.gatech.edu/bme/georgia-tech-emory-peking-university-bme-phd-program|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2016-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014221652/http://www.bme.gatech.edu/bme/georgia-tech-emory-peking-university-bme-phd-program|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Wallace H. Coulter Department of Biomedical Engineering Program|url=https://www.bme.gatech.edu|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106120810/https://bme.gatech.edu/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它和[[南京大学|南京大学]]协作运行[[孔子学院|亚特兰大的孔子学院]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Confucius Institute in Atlanta|url=http://confucius.emory.edu/about/index.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2013-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130120051211/http://confucius.emory.edu/about/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大學与[[韩国科学技术院|韩国科学技术院]]不断加强系际研究伙伴关系<ref>{{cite web|title=Georgia Tech-Emory-KAIST Biomedical Engineering Faculty|url=http://www.kaist.edu/_prog/_board/?mode=V&no=36608&code=en_management5&site_dvs_cd=en&menu_dvs_cd=06070205&skey=&sval=&site_dvs=&GotoPage=|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515152154/http://www.kaist.edu/_prog/_board/?mode=V&no=36608&code=en_management5&site_dvs_cd=en&menu_dvs_cd=06070205&skey=&sval=&site_dvs=&GotoPage=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Summer Biomedical Engineering Workshop in Daejeon, South Korea|url=https://www.bme.gatech.edu/bme/summer-biomedical-engineering-workshop-daejeon-south-korea|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929044654/https://www.bme.gatech.edu/bme/summer-biomedical-engineering-workshop-daejeon-south-korea|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Comparative Investigations of Cp*-Based Group 9 Metal-Catalyzed Direct C–H Amination of Benzamides|url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/om5005868?journalCode=orgnd7|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113143701/http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/om5005868?journalCode=orgnd7|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大學的学生来自美国50个[[美国州份|州]]、6个[[美国领土|领土]]和100多个国家<ref>{{cite web|title= Emory University International Students|url= http://www.emory.edu/home/admission/international.html|accessdate= 2016-10-07|archive-date= 2021-01-07|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210107111240/https://www.emory.edu/home/admission/international.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

[[埃默里医疗集团|埃默里医疗集团]]是喬治亞州最大的医疗集团系统<ref name="about">{{cite web|url=http://www.emoryhealthcare.org/about-us/index.html|title=About Emory Healthcare|author=Emory Healthcare|accessdate=2016年10月21日|archive-date=2011年8月7日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807011430/http://www.emoryhealthcare.org/about-us/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由七座大医院组成，其中包括国际知名的埃默里大学医院和埃默里大学医院中城院区<ref>{{cite web|url=http://health.usnews.com/best-hospitals/area/ga/emory-university-hospital-6380570|accessdate=2016年10月21日|title=Emory University Hospital|archive-date=2015年2月22日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222040651/http://health.usnews.com/best-hospitals/area/ga/emory-university-hospital-6380570|dead-url=no}}</ref>。温希普癌症研究所、[[耶基斯国家灵长类研究中心|耶基斯国家灵长类研究中心]]和其它许多疾病和免疫研究中心也由埃默里大学运行<ref name="cysticfibrosisnewstoday.com">{{cite web|title=Cystic Fibrosis Foundation Grants $1.8 million to Expand the Atlanta CF Research and Development Program|url=http://cysticfibrosisnewstoday.com/2015/07/17/cystic-fibrosis-foundation-grants-1-8-million-expand-atlanta-cf-research-development-program/|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113144520/https://cysticfibrosisnewstoday.com/2015/07/17/cystic-fibrosis-foundation-grants-1-8-million-expand-atlanta-cf-research-development-program/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大学是国家过敏症和传染病研究所的疟疾病原体互动中心和[[美国卫生及公共服务部|美国卫生及公共服务部]]国家埃博拉训练和教育中心的主要组织者<ref name="bizjournals.com">{{cite web|title=Emory University to lead National Ebola Training and Education Center|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/news/2015/07/01/emory-university-to-lead-national-ebola-training.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113144246/http://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/news/2015/07/01/emory-university-to-lead-national-ebola-training.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大学是参加国家过敏症和传染病研究所肺结核研究项目的四所研究单位之一<ref name="NIH Tuberculosis Research Program">{{cite web|title=NIH Tuberculosis Research Program|url=https://www.niaid.nih.gov/news/newsreleases/2015/Pages/TBawards.aspx|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2016-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910055656/https://www.niaid.nih.gov/news/newsreleases/2015/Pages/TBawards.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[国家级公共卫生机构国际联盟|国家级公共卫生机构国际联盟]]（International Association of National Public Health Institutes, IANPHI）的總部位在埃默里大学<ref name="ianphi.org">{{cite web|url=http://www.ianphi.org/whoweare/history.html|title=History|work=ianphi.org|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130428072858/http://www.ianphi.org/whoweare/history.html|archivedate=2013-04-28|accessdate=2016-10-07}}</ref>。[[美國疾病管制與預防中心|美國疾病管制與預防中心]]和[[美国癌症协会|美国癌症协会]]的总部就位于大学校园边上<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.med.emory.edu/about/facilities_affiliations.html|accessdate=2016年10月21日|title=Facilities & Affiliations|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020113152/http://med.emory.edu/about/facilities_affiliations.html|archive-date=2017年10月20日|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。埃默里大学和[[卡特中心|卡特中心]]有伙伴关系<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cartercenter.org/index.html|title=The Carter Center – Waging Peace. Fighting Disease|work=The Carter Center|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106075155/https://www.cartercenter.org/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

埃默里大學的学校基金会财产在美国排第16名<ref name=Forbes>{{cite web|title=''Forbes'': 22 Richest Schools In America|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/ccap/2014/07/30/22-richest-schools-in-america/|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012549/https://www.forbes.com/sites/ccap/2014/07/30/22-richest-schools-in-america/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在全世界是第21富有的<ref>{{cite web|title='The World’s 50 Wealthiest Universities|url=http://www.nonprofitcollegesonline.com/wealthiest-universities-in-the-world/|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211080407/https://www.nonprofitcollegesonline.com/wealthiest-universities-in-the-world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，根据《[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]]》2017年美國大学排行榜排第20名<ref name=USN&WR>{{cite web|title=''U.S. News & World Report'': National University Rankings.|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/rankings/national-universities|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110521210513/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/rankings/national-universities|archivedate=2011-05-21|accessdate=2016-10-07}}</ref>，综合排名第82名。研究生的数量和本科生的数量基本持平。常年錄取率保持在25%上下。[[卡內基高校评估|卡內基高校评估]]把它评为“最高研究活动”。莱顿大学的高校排名里它被称为拥有最高科学成就和[[引文影响|引文影响]]<ref>{{cite web|title=CWTS Leiden Ranking|url=http://www.leidenranking.com/ranking/2015/university?universityId=1168&fieldId=2&periodId=5&fractionalCounting=1&performanceDimension=0&sizeIndependent=True&rankingIndicator=pp_top10&minNPubs=100|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805000023/https://www.leidenranking.com/ranking/2015/university?universityId=1168&fieldId=2&periodId=5&fractionalCounting=1&performanceDimension=0&sizeIndependent=True&rankingIndicator=pp_top10&minNPubs=100|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[国家科学基金会|国家科学基金会]]把它列为美国[[研究開發|研究開發]]支出第36名高的学术机构<ref>{{cite web|title= NSF Rankings by total R&D expenditures|url= https://ncsesdata.nsf.gov/profiles/site?method=rankingBySource&ds=herd|access-date= 2016-10-07|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170113144205/https://ncsesdata.nsf.gov/profiles/site?method=rankingBySource&ds=herd|archive-date= 2017-01-13|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。埃默里大學的研究主要由[[美國聯邦政府|美國聯邦政府]]，尤其是[[國立衛生研究院_(美國)|國立衛生研究院]]支付<ref name="ReferenceB">{{cite web|title=Emory University gets record $572.4M in external research funding in 2015|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/news/2015/09/25/emory-university-gets-record-572-4m-in-external.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2017-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170718113036/https://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/news/2015/09/25/emory-university-gets-record-572-4m-in-external.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1995年埃默里大學被选入由62座美国和加拿大领先研究大学组成的[[美國學院與大學協會|美國學院與大學協會]]<ref name="aau.edu"/>。在體育方面，埃默里大学是[[大學運動聯盟|大學運動聯盟]]（UAA）的成員學校之一。

