卡内基高等教育机构分类把埃默里大學定为“研究活动非常高”。按照[[高等教育紀事報|高等教育紀事報]]埃默里大學是美国大学里平均研究支出第五高的<ref name=Chronicle>{{cite journal|last=Basken|first=Paul|work=The Chronicle of Higher Education|title=UCLA, Eyeing Profits, Entrusts Tech Transfer to Industry Experts|url=http://chronicle.texterity.com/chronicle/20130816a?folio=A12#pg12|date=August 16, 2013|page=A12|journal=|author=|access-date=2016-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108222633/http://chronicle.texterity.com/chronicle/20130816a?folio=A12#pg12|archive-date=2015-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。它是美国公共研究机构里发现新药物和疫苗第四高的<ref name="auto2">{{cite web|title=The Role of Public-Sector Research in the Discovery of Drugs and Vaccines|url=http://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMsa1008268|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028165216/https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMsa1008268|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[基础医药大学联盟|基础医药大学联盟]]把埃默里大學评为所有美国和加拿大对全球健康和研究作出贡献的大学中的第六名<ref name=UAEM>{{cite web|title=''UAEM'':University Global Health Impact Report Card|url=http://globalhealthgrades.org|accessdate=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112013822/http://globalhealthgrades.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年埃默里大學从其它基金机构获得5.724亿美元<ref name="ReferenceC">{{cite web|title=Emory receives record $572.4 million in external research funding for 2015|url=http://news.emory.edu/stories/2015/09/research_funding_2015/campus.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731010459/http://news.emory.edu/stories/2015/09/research_funding_2015/campus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大學是获得[[國立衛生研究院_(美國)|美国國立衛生研究院]]博士前国家研究奖金人数最高的<ref>{{cite web|title=Emory ranks first in the U.S. for students with NIH predoctoral fellowships|url=http://news.emory.edu/stories/2015/03/er_nih_predoctoral_fellowships/campus.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929105652/http://news.emory.edu/stories/2015/03/er_nih_predoctoral_fellowships/campus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

埃默里大學和[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]有紧密的合作。1947年大学向[[美国卫生及公共服务部|美国卫生及公共服务部]]捐献了15公顷地来建筑疾病控制与预防中心的总部<ref name=CDC>{{cite web|title=''CDC'': Our History - Our Story|url=http://www.cdc.gov/about/history/ourstory.htm|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619045405/http://www.cdc.gov/about/history/ourstory.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大學的预防研究中心和受伤控制中心是疾病控制和预防中心资助的<ref>{{cite web|title=Funded Injury Control Research Centers (ICRCs)|url=http://www.cdc.gov/injury/erpo/icrc/emory.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731005450/https://www.cdc.gov/injury/erpo/icrc/emory.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大學的非洲公共卫生安全卓越中心是埃默里大學与疾病控制与预防中心以及国家公共卫生研究所国际协会合作的五年数百万基金项目，其目标是提高低收入国家对卫生威胁的准备和反应<ref>{{cite web|title=African Center for Public Health Security|url=http://news.emory.edu/stories/2015/02/rollins_cdc_partnership_award/campus.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918164842/http://news.emory.edu/stories/2015/02/rollins_cdc_partnership_award/campus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大學全球水安全与疾病控制和预防中心合作应用研究、估价和训练来通过改善获得干净的水、排污和卫生促进全球卫生平等<ref>{{cite web|title=The Safe Water System, Kenya|url=http://www.cdc.gov/safewater/pdf/sws-and-schools-kenya-508c.pdf|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019060513/https://www.cdc.gov/safewater/pdf/SWS-and-schools-Kenya-508c.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Safe Water System|url=http://www.cdc.gov/safewater/resources.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024185535/https://www.cdc.gov/safewater/resources.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由[[比尔及梅琳达·盖茨基金会|比尔及梅琳达·盖茨基金会]]资助的埃默里大學全球卫生研究所与疾病控制和预防中心合作来提高低资源国家的公共卫生基础设施<ref>{{cite web|title=CDC Global Public Health Network|url=http://www.ianphi.org/news/2011/EmoryAndCDCPartner.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515050453/http://www.ianphi.org/news/2011/EmoryAndCDCPartner.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2003年[[嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症|嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症]]爆发后疾病控制和预防中心设立了埃默里大學附属医院隔离单位和检疫站<ref>{{cite web|title=U.S. Quarantine Stations|url=http://www.cdc.gov/quarantine/quarantine-stations-us.html#map|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116060416/https://www.cdc.gov/quarantine/quarantine-stations-us.html#map|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默里大學的隔离和治疗设施在2004年美国埃博拉病毒爆发事件里起了关键作用<ref>{{cite web|title=Cases of Ebola Diagnosed in the United States|url=http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/outbreaks/2014-west-africa/united-states-imported-case.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219214351/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/outbreaks/2014-west-africa/united-states-imported-case.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。疾病控制了预防中心的科学家和管理人员也使埃默里大學免疫晚餐俱乐部的成员，并经常在那里演讲。这个俱乐部每月举办学术会议讨论[[疫苗|疫苗]]研究的进展<ref>{{cite web|title=Emory Vaccine Dinner Club|url=http://www.asm.gtorg.gatech.edu/event/emory-vaccine-dinner-club-2/|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227101242/http://www.asm.gtorg.gatech.edu/event/emory-vaccine-dinner-club-2/|archivedate=2015-02-27|accessdate=2016-10-07}}</ref>。2015年埃默里大學成为疾病控制和预防中心的预防震中项目成员。这个研究项目是由疾病控制和预防中心的卫生质量促进部领导的，它与学术专家一起研究创新的流行病控制和预防措施<ref>{{cite web|title=About the Prevention Epicenters Program|url=http://www.cdc.gov/HAI/epiCenters/about.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018005610/https://www.cdc.gov/hai/epicenters/about.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite web|title=CDC awards Emory University $2.2M grant|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/news/2015/10/05/cdc-awards-emory-university-2-2m-grant.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2017-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702234815/http://www.bizjournals.com/atlanta/news/2015/10/05/cdc-awards-emory-university-2-2m-grant.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年埃默里大學、[[倫敦衛生與熱帶醫學院|倫敦衛生與熱帶醫學院]]、[[印度公共卫生基金会|印度公共卫生基金会]]和[[全印度医学科学研究所|全印度医学科学研究所]]在[[印度|印度]][[新德里|新德里]]创办慢性病症控制中心。其目的在于改善糖尿病、心脏病、癌症、精神病和创伤在印度的预防和治疗<ref>{{cite web|title=Emory supports quest to defeat diabetes in India|url=http://news.emory.edu/stories/2015/10/hspub_defeating_diabetes_in_india/campus.html|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731015002/http://news.emory.edu/stories/2015/10/hspub_defeating_diabetes_in_india/campus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

国家公共卫生研究所国际协会的基地位于埃默里大學。2006年比尔及梅琳达·盖茨基金会授予埃默里大學为期五年的2000玩美元捐款设立了这个协会。2015年比尔及梅琳达·盖茨基金会又授予埃默里大學和疾病控制和预防中心7500万美元创办儿童健康和死亡率防治监测网络<ref>{{cite web|title=Child Health and Mortality Prevention Surveillance Network|url=http://www.gatesfoundation.org/Media-Center/Press-Releases/2015/05/Child-Health-and-Mortality-Prevention-Surveillance-Network|accessdate=2016-10-07|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805085406/https://www.gatesfoundation.org/Media-Center/Press-Releases/2015/05/Child-Health-and-Mortality-Prevention-Surveillance-Network|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
